the israeli armys use of 
plastic bullets to break up palestinian demonstrations is filling 
hospital wards with casualties and prompting calls for tighter 
controls 
victims of the new ammunition including two teenagers treated 
for plastic bullet wounds at ahli arab hospital in gaza city 
