are not supposed to be lethal if fired from at least 70 yards 
however at least four deaths from plastic bullets have been 
reported at shifa hospital in gaza city 
last week dr rustum namari director of the mukassad hospital 
in east jerusalem showed reporters fragments of a plastic bullet 
removed from the brain of a critically injured west bank youth 
