has the potential to cause death said a surgeon at shifa 
hospital who spoke on condition of anonymnity remember too 
that bullets respect no age he added victims he said have 
ranged in age from 7 to 90 
the bullets developed after israeli officials studied use of 
plastic ammunition in france are produced in israel 
similar plastic rounds have been used in northern ireland for 
riot control since 1970 and at least 13 deaths have been 
attributed to them there 
