discipline 
about 74 million people were registered to vote voting is 
mandatory and turnout was heavy across this narrow country wedged 
between the snowcapped andes mountains and the pacific 
anyone who did not vote soon after polls opened at 8 am risked 
a long wait under a glaring spring sun 
men removed their sport coats and sweaters and women standing 
