here is a chronology of major events in the case 
of tawana brawley the wappingers falls teenager who claimed she 
was abducted and raped by a gang of white men a grand jury found 
her story a fabrication 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
nov 28 after disappearing for four days 15yearold tawana 
brawley is found at the apartment complex where her family had 
lived she is in a plastic bag her body smeared with animal feces 
and scrawled with racial slurs according to her family the girl 
was kidnapped and sexually assaulted 
dec 2 fishkill police officer harry crist jr commits 
suicide although he fits the girls description of one of her 
attackers prosecutors later say it is unlikely the death is 
related to the case 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
jan 26 gov mario cuomo names attorney general robert abrams 
special prosecutor in the case but brawley advisers the rev al 
sharpton and attorneys c vernon mason and alton maddox denounce 
the appointment and refuse to cooperate 
feb 10 entertainer bill cosby and a magazine publisher offer 
a 25000 reward for information in the case 
feb 29 a state grand jury is empaneled to investigate 
may 24 tawanas mother glenda brawley on the advice of 
sharpton mason and maddox defies the states first attempt to 
compel testimony from a family member and refuses to appear before 
the grand jury 
june 6 mrs brawley again refuses to testify and is ordered 
jailed for 30 days and fined 250 
june 8 mrs brawley takes religious sanctuary in a new 
york city church 
june 15 former sharpton aide perry mckinnon says the brawley 
case is a pack of lies designed to advance the political agenda 
of sharpton mason and maddox sharpton and the lawyers call 
mckinnon a liar 
june 16 abrams says he is investigating the possibility of a 
hoax in the case 
june 20 selfdescribed surveillance expert samuel mcclease 
says that on sharptons orders he secretly tape recorded 
conversations of brawley advisers discussing misgivings about the 
case the advisers denounce mcclease 
june 21 federal officials direct mcclease to appear before a 
federal grand jury looking into the brawley affair 
june 25 mcclease turns blank tapes over to authorities and is 
charged with obstruction and perjury 
aug 16 the brawley advisers reaffirm their stand miss 
brawley will not obey any subpoena the subpoena is later rescinded 
sept 21 sharpton confirms reports the brawleys have moved to 
virginia 
sept 27 the new york times citing sources reports the grand 
jury has overwhelming evidence miss brawley lied 
sept 28 miss brawley appearing in newark nj says i am 
not a liar and i am not crazy i just want justice she refuses 
to answer questions 
oct 6 grand jury report is issued calling miss brawleys 
story a fabrication abrams files charges against mason and maddox 
with a legal review panel announces that sharpton is under 
investigation clears crist and pagones 
</TEXT>
