compensatory damages 
the complaint was brought under the false claims act which 
allows private parties to bring suit on behalf of the government 
and gives the government the right to join a case 
assistant attorney general john bolton said the justice 
department has decided there is insufficient basis for it to enter 
the matter now 
the government could enter the suit at a later time 
in a related matter the justice department sued northrop in 
august 1987 for 3 million for failing to properly test a component 
of the mx the justice department suit followed a private suit 
