ashland oil inc thursday entered a not guilty 
plea and asked for a jury trial on criminal negligence charges in 
the jan 2 tank collapse that fouled two major rivers with diesel 
fuel 
a spokesman for the kentuckybased company which publicly 
admitted errors that figured in the collapse declined to say 
